featureType.name: HEATMAP_habitat_obs_PHYSICAL
featureType.title: HEATMAP - weighted coverage and density of physical seafloor observations for habitat mapping validation
featureType.abstract:
This layer represents a heatmap of spatial coverage of sediment samples derived from GA's Marine Sediments Database. Weightings have been applied to samples according to their suitability for validating seafloor habitat mapping:
(1) 2x weighting for observations <3 years old; 1.5x for 3-5 years, 1x for >5 years (2) 2x weighting for analysed samples (3) deployment points separated by less than 5m have been aggregated and collapsed into a single point (ie no spatial duplication)
